item.title: Bringing Water to a Drought-Stricken Community in Tanzania
item.description:
Bringing Water to a Drought-Stricken Community in Tanzania

Miami Dolphins wide receiver Greg Jennings and other NFL stars join the Starkey team in Tanzania to help give the gift of hearing. During their mission they also help build a well for a local Maasai community that is struggling to access one of life's most basic necessities-clean water.
